

BAHIN

   biglang paghinga mula sa ilong
   bahín
   sneeze

   bumahín
   to sneeze

   Ang lakas ng bahing mo!
   Your sneeze is so strong (=loud).

   Takpan mo ang iyong bibig kung babahin ka.
   Cover your mouth when you sneeze.
     __________________________________________________________________

   The more colloquial word for ‘sneeze’ is atsing / hatsing.
